<h1><%= @destination.name %></h1>

Five Most Recent Posts:
<ul>
    <% @destination.most_recent_posts[0..4].each do |post| %>
    <li><%= post.title %></li>
    <% end %>
</ul>

Featured Post:
<ul>
    <li><%= link_to @destination.featured_post.title, post_path(@destination.featured_post) %></li>
</ul>

Average Age of Bloggers that have written about <%= @destination.name %>:
<ul>
    <li><%= @destination.average_age %></li>
</ul>